## 🛡️ Vulnerabilities & Resolutions

*   **Vulnerability:** Weak local storage configurations allowed fast acquisition of credential tables under low operational hurdles.
*   **Remediation:** Enforce modern NTLM structural security, completely deactivate legacy SMBv1 configurations network-wide, and implement strict account access compartmentalization rules to prevent lateral context shifting.
